creator: BH App Development Ltd
descriptionHtml:
App for ZEN Training clients to use to chart their progress of the results in 1-1 sessions, small group and bootcamp.

Clients can keep a database of their forms which include a conformed consent, par-q, lifestyle questionnaires and their contracts.

Clients can access both individual programmes and also generic programmes for bootcamp through the use of videos and guides through written instructions.

Habit based guides for clients to follow with their nutrition.
descriptionShort: Zen Training Teddington - app for clients to chart their progress in sessions
title: Zen Body
